%%{init: {'theme': 'base'}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    participant C as 📱 Customer
    participant APP as Mobile App
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant BFF as BFF
    participant PO as Payment Orchestrator
    participant ID as Identity Service
    participant FS as Feature Store
    participant FI as Fraud Inference
    participant EX as Explainability
    participant DO as Decision Orchestrator
    participant K as Kafka
    participant SCA as Step-Up Auth
    participant HRQ as Human Review Queue
    participant CC as Contact Centre
    participant COP as AML/Fraud Co-Pilot
    participant LLM as LLM Gateway
    participant MF as Mainframe Facade
    participant AU as Audit Service
    participant N as Notification

    C->>APP: Initiate UPI ₹2,40,000
    APP->>GW: HTTPS + Bearer Token [2ms]
    GW->>BFF: mTLS [2ms]
    BFF->>PO: Route payment [2ms]
    
    PO->>ID: Validate session [3ms]
    ID-->>PO: OK (OIDC valid)
    
    PO->>FS: Get features [8ms p99]
    FS-->>PO: txn_velocity, device_fp, payee_risk
    
    PO->>FI: Score transaction [gRPC]
    FI->>EX: Compute SHAP [8ms]
    EX-->>FI: Top 3 factors
    FI-->>PO: Score: 0.72 (HOLD) + Attribution [55ms total]
    
    PO->>DO: Route decision
    DO-->>PO: Confirm HOLD (new beneficiary + borderline)
    
    PO->>K: Publish events [async, 3ms]
    Note over K: afg.fraud.in.scores<br/>afg.fraud.in.decisions
    
    PO->>SCA: Trigger biometric challenge
    SCA->>APP: Push notification
    APP->>C: Request fingerprint
    C->>APP: Confirm biometric
    APP->>SCA: SCA success
    SCA-->>PO: Authenticated
    
    Note over PO: Score still borderline → Escalate
    
    PO->>HRQ: Escalate (score=0.72, context) [30s]
    HRQ->>CC: Assign to agent
    
    CC->>COP: "Is this suspicious?"
    COP->>LLM: Query with PII redacted
    LLM->>MF: Get account context [15ms cache]
    MF-->>LLM: Corporate relationship data
    LLM-->>COP: "Low risk - verified merchant" + citations [8s]
    COP-->>CC: Assessment + evidence
    
    CC->>HRQ: APPROVE (rationale: verified merchant)
    HRQ->>PO: Release transaction
    PO->>AU: Full audit chain [7-year retention]
    Note over AU: Score • Factors • SCA • Co-pilot • Decision
    PO->>N: Payment released
    N->>C: "₹2,40,000 sent to [beneficiary]"
